Title: As a user I can create new order data with a valid path and body request
As a user I can't create new order with an invalid path
As a user I can't create new order data if content field blank request
As a user I can get all orders data with a valid path
As a user I can't get all orders with an invalid path
As a user I can get order by ID data with a valid path
As a user I cannot get order data with an invalid ID (by entering the ID numbers, letters & symbols at the same time)
As a user I cannot get order data with an invalid ID (by entering an ID number that does not yet exist in the database)
